-Rules of the Tavern-

*We serve Alcohol here. A lot of alcohol. As such no children are allowed within the Tavern. They will only be allowed through if their parents have purchased a room in the inn.

*No violence will be tolerated within. We have bouncers and we will use them.

*This is a Republic bar on a Republic world. All are welcome but if you enter you understand this and leave your politics at the door.

-Menu-

The Oceanside Inn & Tavern - Home of The One Sauce and the Famous Krayt Steak Challenge.

Krayt Steak al la Bob - 50 lbs of Krayt steak in 50 minutes or less, smothered in The One Sauce. Winners receive a tee shirt and their picture on our wall of fame.

Tossed Salad - Fresh grown and locally sourced produce!

Pasta with Tomato Wine Sauce - Delicious and made to order!

Fish of the Day - Caught by our resident Chef and prepared fresh!

Menu items change daily, check inside with our friendly staff to find out what's cooking today.
